Package org.wmn4j.notation

Class PartBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.wmn4j.notation.PartBuilder
public class PartBuilder extends Object
Builder for building Part objects.

Instances of this class are not thread-safe.

    • getMeasureCount

      public int getMeasureCount()
      Returns the number of measures in the longest staff in this builder.

      For a single staff part the returned number is the number of measures. For a part with multiple staves the returned number is the number of measures in the staff with the largest number of measures.

      Returns:
      the number of measures in the longest staff in this builder
